.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n\n<p>設定でアイコンを指定しなかった場合に使用されるアイコンです。</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"デフォルトグループ\"><a href=\"https://github.com/technote-space/add-richtext-toolbar-button#%E3%83%87%E3%83%95%E3%82%A9%E3%83%AB%E3%83%88%E3%82%B0%E3%83%AB%E3%83%BC%E3%83%97\"></a>デフォルトグループ<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#デフォルトグループ\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" fill=\"none\" color=\"#131996\"><path d=\"M7.93517339,13.7795989 L15.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n\n<p>設定でグループ名を指定しなかった場合に使用されるグループ名です。</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"テスト用文章\"><a href=\"https://github.com/technote-space/add-richtext-toolbar-button#%E3%83%86%E3%82%B9%E3%83%88%E7%94%A8%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0\"></a>テスト用文章<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#テスト用文章\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" fill=\"none\" color=\"#131996\"><path d=\"M7.93517339,13.7795989 L15.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n\n<p>設定画面や一覧でテスト表示用に使用される文章を指定します。</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"要件\"><a href=\"https://github.com/technote-space/add-richtext-toolbar-button#%E8%A6%81%E4%BB%B6\"></a>要件<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#要件\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" fill=\"none\" color=\"#131996\"><path d=\"M7.93517339,13.7795989 L15.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n\n<ul><li>PHP 5.6 以上</li><li>WordPress 5.0.3 以上</li></ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"スクリーンショット\"><a href=\"https://github.com/technote-space/add-richtext-toolbar-button#%E3%82%B9%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%83%E3%83%88\"></a>スクリーンショット<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#スクリーンショット\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" fill=\"none\" color=\"#131996\"><path d=\"M7.93517339,13.7795989 L15.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/technote-space/my-blog-assets/main/uploads/2019/02/201902150444.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/technote-space/my-blog-assets/main/uploads/2019/02/201902150444.png\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1024\" data-link=\"/add-richtext-toolbar-button/attachment/201902150444\" class=\"wp-image-1024\"></a><figcaption>Gutenbergエディタ</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/technote-space/my-blog-assets/main/uploads/2019/02/screenshot-2.png\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/technote-space/my-blog-assets/main/uploads/2019/02/screenshot-2.png\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1064\" data-link=\"/add-richtext-toolbar-button/attachment/screenshot-2-2\" class=\"wp-image-1064\"></a><figcaption>サイドバー</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/technote-space/my-blog-assets/main/uploads/2019/02/screenshot-3-1024x642.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/technote-space/my-blog-assets/main/uploads/2019/02/screenshot-3-1024x642.png\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1065\" data-link=\"/add-richtext-toolbar-button/attachment/screenshot-3-3\" class=\"wp-image-1065\"></a><figcaption>設定追加</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/technote-space/my-blog-assets/main/uploads/2019/02/201902150436-1024x648.png\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/technote-space/my-blog-assets/main/uploads/2019/02/201902150436-1024x648.png\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1023\" data-link=\"/add-richtext-toolbar-button/attachment/201902150436\" class=\"wp-image-1023\"></a><figcaption>設定一覧</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/technote-space/my-blog-assets/main/uploads/2019/02/screenshot-5.png\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/technote-space/my-blog-assets/main/uploads/2019/02/screenshot-5.png\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1066\" data-link=\"/add-richtext-toolbar-button/attachment/screenshot-5\" class=\"wp-image-1066\"></a><figcaption>ダッシュボード</figcaption></figure></li></ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"注意点\">注意点<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#注意点\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" fill=\"none\" color=\"#131996\"><path d=\"M7.93517339,13.7795989 L15.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n\n<p>記事の一覧など、投稿ページ以外では設定で追加したスタイルは適用されません。</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"既知の問題\">既知の問題<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#既知の問題\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" fill=\"none\" color=\"#131996\"><path d=\"M7.93517339,13.7795989 L15.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n\n<p>Gutenberg側にバグがあり、文章に適用済みの設定のクラス名を後から変更したり設定自体を削除した場合に他のデザインが適用される場合があります。</p>\n\n<div class=\"blog-card\"><iframe src=\"https://blog-card-ten.vercel.app/card/https%3A%2F%2Ftechnote.space%2Fwordpress%2Fgutenberg-richtext-bug?id=blog-card-gqjcv8d4lg&#x26;referrer=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnote.space%2Fposts%2Fwpxml-add-richtext-toolbar-button%2F\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" loading=\"lazy\" data-id=\"blog-card-gqjcv8d4lg\"></iframe></div>\n\n<p>設定のクラス名を変更したいときは以下のいずれかを行ったほうがよいです。</p>\n\n<ul><li>すでに適用したものをすべて外してから変更する</li><li>適用済みの設定の「ツールバーボタンが有効かどうか」を外して、追加したいクラスを持つ設定を新規追加する</li></ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"要望バグ報告等\">要望・バグ報告等<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#要望バグ報告等\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" vi